---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const imgBase = "https://identitysummitfiles.blob.core.windows.net/cis-images";
---

<Layout title="Cloud Identity Summit 2023">
    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 w-full flex-grow">
        
        <div class="mb-12">
            <a href="/archive" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold transition bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                ← Back to Archive
            </a>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-8">
            Cloud Identity Summit 2023
        </h1>

        <div class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16 space-y-6">
            <p>The forth Cloud Identity Summit took place on September 07, 2023. After our first hybrid event last year we going format with this format and of course continue to offer it free of charge. The location were made available to us by DICE (Debeka Innovation Center) in Koblenz near to the Mosel.</p>
            <p>Furthermore, adesso SE and glueckkanja-gab supported us again as partners - thank you! Without them we would not have been able to offer this conference free of charge for the participants. We change the conference a bit were able to offer ten sessions in two parallel tracks were held on site and additionally streamed to participants all over the world. The subsequent roundtable with all experts rounded off the program.</p>
            <p>We would like to thank our speakers, without whom we would not have been able to offer the rich and informative program! We were very happy that we were finally able to meet in person and had a lot of fun together.</p>
        </div>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">Agenda & Speakers</h2>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">9:50 am (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Deep dive into the Zero Trust journey : Securing your Azure Ad with our Zero Trust Approach !</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Seyfallah Tagrerout, Jean-Francois (Jeff) Aprea</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">9:50 am (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Empowering Digital Identity: A Journey into Decentralized Trust Systems</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Stefan van der Wiele</span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">11:00 am (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Monitoring and Reporting on Activities and Security in Microsoft Entra Azure AD</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Jan Vidar Elven</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">11:00 am (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">The future of customer identity with Microsoft Entra</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Daniel Krzyczkowski</span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">12:10 pm (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">From (tier) zero to cloud hero: How to pwn Azure AD from on-prem</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Fabian Bader</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">12:10 pm (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Azure AD Identity Governance - What do your users do with their access</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Nicki Borell</span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">2:20 pm (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Implementing and building advanced Microsoft Entra Id Conditional Access scenarios</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Kenneth van Surksum</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">2:20 pm (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Just apply the basics in your Azure AD tenant!</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Sander Berkouwer, Raymond Comvalius</span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">3:30 pm (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Walk the walk - explore ways to ensure strong authentication in real life scenarios</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Christopher Brumm</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">3:30 pm (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Seamless cross-tenant application access with Entra Azure AD Cross-Tenant sync</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Anton Staykov</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>